name: Dicktator Launcher
description:
A game where you can launch dictators straight to hell!

GooglePlay censored it, but here we go again: Dicktator Launcher is back, and now without silly adds!!!

Hitler, Stalin, Franco, Ghandi... a lot of despicable bastards to choose among and smash epicly!

Launch your favorite Dicktator far away and avoid tricky traps in order to succeed.

Don’t let anyone tell you what you can and can’t play!!
